{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish the effective Tax rate of 60% on income between \u00a3100,000 and \u00a3125,140",
        "additional_details": "We believe an effective Tax rate of 60% on income between \u00a3100,000 and \u00a3125,140 is punitive on individuals and certain professions and discourages extra work and career development.",
        "background": "We want the Government to abolish the effective Tax rate of 60% on income between \u00a3100,000 and \u00a3125,140, replacing it with a Tax band of 45% on income over \u00a3100,000 and removing the tapered withdrawal of Personal Allowance.",
